In:
https://docs.saltstack.com/en/develop/topics/installation/rhel.html#installation-rhel-repo

The yum repo is defined with the variable: $releasever, which expands to:  '7Server'

```
baseurl=https://repo.saltstack.com/yum/rhel$releasever
```

But the actual repo seems to be on: '7'

https://repo.saltstack.com/yum/rhel7/repodata/
